<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Profilim | TuMeal</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background: #f6f8fa;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    }
    .brand {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #2c3e50;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }
    .brand .logo {
      color: #ff6b35;
      margin-right: 8px;
    }
    .profile-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(44,62,80,0.08);
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem 2rem;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 3rem auto 2rem auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .profile-avatar {
      width: 90px;
      height: 90px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      border: 4px solid #ff6b35;
    }
    .profile-name {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }
    .profile-email {
      color: #7f8c8d;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }
    .profile-id {
      color: #ff6b35;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
    .profile-btns .btn {
      margin: 0 0.5rem 0.5rem 0.5rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      padding: 10px 24px;
    }
    .btn-orange {
      background: #ff6b35;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-orange:hover {
      background: #e55d2a;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .btn-outline-orange {
      border: 2px solid #ff6b35;
      color: #ff6b35;
      background: #fff;
    }
    .btn-outline-orange:hover {
      background: #ff6b35;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .comment-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(44,62,80,0.06);
      padding: 1.2rem 1.2rem 1rem 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
    .comment-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }
    .comment-avatar {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      margin-right: 1rem;
    }
    .comment-name {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-right: 0.7rem;
    }
    .comment-meal {
      color: #ff6b35;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-right: 0.7rem;
    }
    .comment-date {
      color: #7f8c8d;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .comment-rating {
      color: #f1c40f;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-left: auto;
    }
    .comment-text {
      color: #2c3e50;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #2c3e50;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 2rem 0 1rem 0;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #ff6b35;
      margin: 0 8px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer a:hover {
      color: #fff;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/www/common/navbar') %>
  <div class="container mt-3 mb-4">
    <div class="profile-card">
      <img src="https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=Ahmet+Yilmaz&background=ececec&color=2c3e50" class="profile-avatar" alt="Ahmet Yılmaz">
      <div class="profile-name">Ahmet Yılmaz</div>
      <div class="profile-email">ahmet.yilmaz@universite.edu.tr</div>
      <div class="profile-id">Öğrenci No: 20231234</div>
      <div class="profile-btns mb-2">
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-orange"><i class="fa-solid fa-history me-2"></i>Yorum Geçmişim</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-orange"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-edit me-2"></i>Profili Düzenle</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h4 class="mb-3 mt-4 fw-bold text-center" style="color:#2c3e50;">Yorumlarım</h4>
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-7">
        <div class="comment-card">
          <div class="comment-header">
            <img src="https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=Ahmet+Yilmaz&background=ececec&color=2c3e50" class="comment-avatar" alt="Ahmet Yılmaz">
            <span class="comment-name">Ahmet Yılmaz</span>
            <span class="comment-meal">Düğün Çorbası</span>
            <span class="comment-date">5 saat önce</span>
            <span class="comment-rating ms-auto">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="comment-text">Bugünün düğün çorbası gerçekten harika olmuş! Özellikle yoğurt oranı ve kıvamı tam kararında, nohutlar da çok iyi pişmiş. Ellerinize sağlık!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="comment-card">
          <div class="comment-header">
            <img src="https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=Ahmet+Yilmaz&background=ececec&color=2c3e50" class="comment-avatar" alt="Ahmet Yılmaz">
            <span class="comment-name">Ahmet Yılmaz</span>
            <span class="comment-meal">Mercimek Çorbası</span>
            <span class="comment-date">1 gün önce</span>
            <span class="comment-rating ms-auto">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="comment-text">Mercimek çorbası biraz tuzlu olmuştu ama genel olarak lezzetliydi.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="comment-card">
          <div class="comment-header">
            <img src="https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=Ahmet+Yilmaz&background=ececec&color=2c3e50" class="comment-avatar" alt="Ahmet Yılmaz">
            <span class="comment-name">Ahmet Yılmaz</span>
            <span class="comment-meal">Tavuklu Sultan Kebabı</span>
            <span class="comment-date">2 gün önce</span>
            <span class="comment-rating ms-auto">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="comment-text">Tavuklu sultan kebabı favorim! Her zamanki gibi çok lezzetliydi.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%- include('../partials/www/common/footer') %>
</body>
</html> 